所謂<br />\n<br />\n要求: DSE ~23分 + 面試<br />\n起薪: $30K (4年後畢業)<br />\n優點: 人工高, 專業人士, 移民加分<br />\n缺點: 俾埋大仔睇唔起話你走後門<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170522/photo/0522-00176-014h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170522%2Fphoto%2F0522-00176-014h1.jpg&h=8ea507a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第1名: COMPUTER SCIENCE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n冇錯...就係IT狗...係咪估唔到呢<br />\n你可以唔信 事實係讀電腦的確可以撈得唔錯<br />\n要穩定既, 老電年年都請好多人<br />\n想搞START UP既, 識寫基本CODE可以幫你慳唔少錢<br />\n返工邊扮工邊炒股炒IPHONE是常識吧<br />\n<br />\nIT拎第一既原因係低分數, 高潛力<br />\n讀HD上DEGREE又得<br />\n就算好唔好彩失業你都可以接freelance<br />\nBTW平時係公司唔好得罪D IT佬<br />\n你返工上過咩網呢D基本野佢一定知<br />\n<br />\n要求: DSE ~10-25分 (視乎院校名氣)<br />\n起薪: $15-30K (4年後畢業)<br />\n優點: 人工OK, 專業人士, 移民加分, 高潛力<br />\n缺點: 俾人笑係IT狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.nicholas.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/14359217_175861116185690_1428497626800145390_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.nicholas.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F14359217_175861116185690_1428497626800145390_n.jpg&h=4c427c22&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇乜幾可可以剩係教PE，唔洗教書都大把行政野你做，另外PE通常要負責埋帶隊比賽，星期六日你都冇埋，因為比賽通常就係喺星期六日，冇比賽，都要訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識揀一定唔揀PE<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7b7f4980cbae6d20d066d45cdb2fe741ae4314","tid":326714,"uid":129186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"Thei除左civil外, Surveying都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0665de233e52dd6a4a210eb06835ae71976a1469","tid":326714,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Thei除左civil外, Surveying都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsurvey都唔錯<br />\n有資格考牌"},{"pid":"25941e1145d3d9b9df22d43e2e7eaccc7946e84f","tid":326714,"uid":25377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"又推人入civil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆煲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e3b35e2073152e5f1080ddfaddebc84dd36c0f","tid":326714,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又推人入civil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆煲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363c8d97e5713bc2325e81daa25488f6b7f4687a","tid":326714,"uid":98365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"Survey year3 入未認住wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd1dedeb0140ee80fb18c4825d18872c0b5b855","tid":326714,"uid":64963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個PO咁多正評<br />\n繼續出<br />\n<br />\n今次想講既就係性價比高既科目<br />\n特登係JUPAS過左先出,廢事擾敵啦<br />\n眼利既連登仔應該會見到今次係講大專, 而唔係大學<br />\n事關有D撚屌好鐘意捉你唔係讀&quot;U&quot;黎講<br />\n所以我都係執返正<br />\n<br />\n點都好, 我都唔係咁重視個學士是否大學頒授<br />\n總之搵到錢就係好degree<br />\n<br />\n------------<br />\n<br />\n第5名: Bed (Ied)<br />\nSOR 都係鐘意叫返教院 好聽D<br />\n雖然成日話文科乞食 但以呢個分數有八大讀係抵屌<br />\n出黎教書/一般文職考政府工都唔成問題<br />\n推薦揀PE, 體育阿SIR最得閒, 到時搭單教多科都唔大work load<br />\n同埋定期有運動做下 放下dopamine 個人會開心D<br />\n冇咁易自殺死<br />\n加上777上任放水去教育界, 你地識做啦<br />\n<br />\n要求: DSE ~20-22分 <br />\n起薪: $20-30K (4年後畢業)<br />\n優點: 人工高, 假多<br />\n缺點: 教畜, 壓力大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3Aa7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3Aa7d.jpg&h=2bbb6177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第4名: CIVIL (THEi)<br />\n土木工程係全世界黎講都係頂尖學科<br />\n宜家讀THEI都可以CHARTERED<br />\n加上VTC人脈夠 搵工唔成問題<br />\n好多人擔心十大基建玩完會爆<br />\n經濟大環境真係好難講<br />\n但19分都有當年AL 2A既civil讀 仲可以要求D咩?<br />\n<br />\n要求: DSE ~19分 <br />\n起薪: $20K (4年後畢業)<br />\n優點: 人工ok, 專業人士, 移民加分<br />\n缺點: 有需要到戶外工作<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/FmHaE_Sw2Fg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FFmHaE_Sw2Fg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=37140087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第3名: GEN NURS (OU&gt;TWC/CIHE)<br />\n護理行業絕對佔一席位<br />\n食正人口老化條水<br />\n香港廢老只會愈多愈多<br />\n加上佢地長命, 你想佢地突然大量暴斃機率係接近零<br />\nHA, 老人院都請RN<br />\n加上在學有得視姦學護淫腳+移民加分<br />\n穩奪第二<br />\n<br />\n要求: DSE ~20分 + 面試<br />\n起薪: $35K (4年後畢業)<br />\n優點: 人工高, 專業人士, 移民加分<br />\n缺點: 工作環境差, 需輪班工作<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.face.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/face/148/640pixfolder/W948-118/c28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.face.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2Fface%2F148%2F640pixfolder%2FW948-118%2Fc28.jpg&h=662c3db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2名: 東華醫療科 (RT, MLS, OT)<br />\n輔助醫療 同NURS近似<br />\n人工低D但唔使返SHIFT<br />\n老牌NGO東華三院出力支持<br />\n舊登連登愈反愈勁<br />\n屌下屌下三科都拎哂牌 下年三科都會入sssdp<br />\n可惜已通天 太多人知推高左收生分數<br />\n性價比低左<br />\n唯一唔好既係要俾理大仔串<br />\n俾人串唔係問題 人地講咩又有乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n要求: DSE ~23分 + 面試<br />\n起薪: $30K (4年後畢業)<br />\n優點: 人工高, 專業人士, 移民加分<br />\n缺點: 俾埋大仔睇唔起話你走後門<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170522/photo/0522-00176-014h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170522%2Fphoto%2F0522-00176-014h1.jpg&h=8ea507a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第1名: COMPUTER SCIENCE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n冇錯...就係IT狗...係咪估唔到呢<br />\n你可以唔信 事實係讀電腦的確可以撈得唔錯<br />\n要穩定既, 老電年年都請好多人<br />\n想搞START UP既, 識寫基本CODE可以幫你慳唔少錢<br />\n返工邊扮工邊炒股炒IPHONE是常識吧<br />\n<br />\nIT拎第一既原因係低分數, 高潛力<br />\n讀HD上DEGREE又得<br />\n就算好唔好彩失業你都可以接freelance<br />\nBTW平時係公司唔好得罪D IT佬<br />\n你返工上過咩網呢D基本野佢一定知<br />\n<br />\n要求: DSE ~10-25分 (視乎院校名氣)<br />\n起薪: $15-30K (4年後畢業)<br />\n優點: 人工OK, 專業人士, 移民加分, 高潛力<br />\n缺點: 俾人笑係IT狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.nicholas.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/14359217_175861116185690_1428497626800145390_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.nicholas.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F14359217_175861116185690_1428497626800145390_n.jpg&h=4c427c22&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIt 都叫性價比高？it狗出到去咩都要識，起薪1萬五 ，但要識百尻幾樣野，仲要不停keep 住學新野，dup code既辛苦到仆街，天天玩腦力與眼力的鍛練，仲要年年都要面對freshgrad 既競爭"},{"pid":"234a6dd58cac37badd18d6034e64c6aadcdb6284","tid":326714,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"in東大we柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee06d8df25a3fce53585f2043470de207978253","tid":326714,"uid":15753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"Bed都要5個㗎阿哥......"},{"pid":"b5a295d564803644df08fc49556d0d25b7fd69de","tid":326714,"uid":15753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Bed都要5年㗎阿哥......</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6c05589e92c015c804c745bc3a48cdb640ddab37","tid":326714,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"EIE 出路多人工高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc220fe2dccad02dc954456c8773bec6fe76ed8","tid":326714,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"睇2-5都ok，但係第一... IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評上一頁"},{"pid":"0642e3d5b76d5ee691e9c5e263de3aa066b0a533","tid":326714,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T